_:N46b7f044639146cba82ada2829b63520 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Graham Razey was appointed Deputy Further Education (FE) Commissioner in December 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He has worked in the education sector for over 31 years, including as Chief Executive of East Kent College Group for 15 years.</p>\n\n<p>Graham also has previous experience as a:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>National Leader of Further Education</li>\n  <li>member of the Department for Education Principal’s Reference Group</li>\n  <li>chair of a multi-academy trust</li>\n  <li>board member on several education, skills and community organisations</li>\n</ul>\n" .
_:N46b7f044639146cba82ada2829b63520 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/Person> .
